textBeforeTable: These skins are a tribute to a champion that underwent a significant visual upgrade to remember their old aesthetic look. They were released with the Champion's relaunch and were free for owners that had owned the champion before hand. If the champion was not previously owned it was put on sale for two weeks before being retired to the Legacy Vault. Traditional Lee Sin is available in the League of Legends store as a permanent skin.
